##### 视频采集

```bash
# 没有 num-buffers 选项则会一直在采集视频，要停下则只有按 ctrl + c
gst-launch-1.0 v4l2src num-buffers=150 device=/dev/video1 ! video/x-raw, width=1280, height=720 ! waylandsink
```
